title: The Sims 4 Kids Room, Romantic Garden and Movie Hangout Update
description:
NEW UPDATE for the previous ALL IN ONE installer that I have put together (being that one a requirement for this to work).

Just copy and paste the files as instructed in my video (link inside the torrent, in case TPB removes it from below, or go to YouTube and search for KMYOscPanXE)!




CONTENT INCLUDED IN THE PREVIOUS RELEASE
(Required to be installed for this version)

The Sims 4 (Base Game)
Get to Work
Get Together
Outdoor Retreat
Spa Day
Luxury Party Stuff
Perfect Patio Stuff
Cool Kitchen Stuff
Spooky Stuff
Digital Deluxe Upgrade
Holiday Celebration Pack

CONTENT INCLUDED IN THIS UPDATE!

Kids Room Stuff
Romantic Garden Stuff
Movie Hangout Stuff
Update of Base Game to 1.20

NOT INCLUDED (YET)
Dine Out

If you don't have Get Together yet, download the required Base Game with Get Together and Previous DLC and install it.

Thanks for the likes and comments, and thanks to Games4theWorld and the Reloaded Group for producing this, so I could test and repack for you! Please help me SEED!!!
